2026-06-10 11:59):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 商航也没完吧 周五催化加上调整幅度也差不多了[/quote]<br/><br/>血包之一", "lou": 3061, "content_length": 13, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 871241573, "postdatetimestamp": 1781064362}, {"pid": 871243622, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 112, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 12:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871242035,45974302,6906]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61395264]村上吹树[/uid] (2026-06-10 12:03):[/b]<br/><br/>一堆人追着我问lml，首先呢，这部分仓位我本来就是拿来做防御和短线的，今天觉得雅克不错，我就切换进去，试试超额，说不定明天就把我埋了，lml大涨，都是有可能的。我只是说下我的操作，不要一个劲儿问我啊，烦啊……觉得我误导你们…那就一开始就不要跟……都是成年人哈……[/quote]<br/>现在可是下跌通道<br/>他们根本不知道下跌通道提前说还能盈利的这种实力到底是什么程度。<br/>正常情况是  我买了 然后叫他们去追 然后他们被挂起来 我卖了<br/>这样才是正常的<br/><br/>现在这个楼里给的策略是不正常的。", "lou": 3062, "content_length": 181, "reply_to": 871242035, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781064963}, {"pid": 871245059, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 12:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871244766,45974302,6909]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62832396]太太OvO贴贴[/uid] (2026-06-10 12:25):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，我想请问一下<br/>缩圈的时候，核心的分支细分为什么不是平盘抗跌反而是有所表现呢？这样搞里面主力资金不会压力很大吗？<br/>还是说趁机从散户或者量化那里拿筹码？[/quote]<br/>因为 缩圈 资金过于集中", "lou": 3063, "content_length": 25, "reply_to": 871244766, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781065703}, {"pid": 871250469, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 146, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 13:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我觉得今天还行啊  不用嚎 我看看今天能不能点个低点<br/>不过可能你们不喜欢看 哈哈", "lou": 3064, "content_length": 70, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781068740}, {"pid": 871251368, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 92, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 13:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "那种锂电锂矿小金属的 我觉得这两天的调整别割肉<br/>资金要搅动这边的血包。", "lou": 3065, "content_length": 66, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781069234}, {"pid": 871252160, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 13:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871251912,45974302,6918]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60621194]HoshiZorA_Z[/uid] (2026-06-10 13:32):[/b]<br/><br/>科创铁盒已经快入水了[s:ac:哭笑]<br/>这波早上又不知道套了多少人[/quote]<br/>昨天都直接预演了。。。当然 我是猜的", "lou": 3066, "content_length": 39, "reply_to": 871251912, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781069658}, {"pid": 871252278, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 66, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 13:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871252209,45974302,6919]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62832396]太太OvO贴贴[/uid] (2026-06-10 13:34):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大能不能教教大家为什么这个时候不是低点？<br/>是时间没到吗？[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>因为我说不是就不是", "lou": 3067, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 871252209, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781069723}, {"pid": 871254899, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 69, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 13:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871254525,45974302,6923]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60968944]克里斯玛雅[/uid] (2026-06-10 13:54):[/b]<br/><br/>[b]Reply to [pid=871254378,45974302,6923]Reply[/pid] Post by [uid=67074240]强悍的小绵羊[/uid] (2026-06-10 13:53)大逃亡了[/quote]<br/>这种位置割肉就跟前天我喊低点的时候割肉一样这么惨", "lou": 3068, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 871254525, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781071049}, {"pid": 871255339, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 107, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天的低点不具备操作性 资金切换出去了", "lou": 3069, "content_length": 36, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781071281}, {"pid": 871256197, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 131, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们不懂 指数低点 要配合能挣钱才行<br/>拉的不是我的方向 那就没有做的必要性<br/>你们没搞懂一点  重要的不是 不跌了  而是  买了要能涨", "lou": 3070, "content_length": 110, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781071715}, {"pid": 871256619, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 49, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:11", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871256501,45974302,6929]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=11354050]msjwhmxc123[/uid] (2026-06-10 14:11):[/b]<br/><br/>说明这个底是国家队拖出来的 没钱来追科技吧([/quote]<br/>目前没发现GJD主动买盘。", "lou": 3071, "content_length": 28, "reply_to": 871256501, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781071917}, {"pid": 871256918, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 77, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "资金去搅动金融 锂电锂矿金属。我没什么兴趣。不是来做科技的我都不想买<br/>我明天再考虑了", "lou": 3072, "content_length": 80, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781072061}, {"pid": 871257436, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871257019,45974302,6930]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66993211]我的钱哪去了[/uid] (2026-06-10 14:15):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大发之前观察到锂矿又拉了一根小直线，但是这个力度太小了吧，真的能搅动起来吗[/quote]<br/>很难跟你解释这么详细的盘口 你看结果就行了", "lou": 3073, "content_length": 45, "reply_to": 871257019, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781072323}, {"pid": 871257858, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 84, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:21", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871257658,45974302,6930]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=6313142]暮残[/uid] (2026-06-10 14:20):[/b]<br/><br/>今天微红，心满意足[s:ac:愁][/quote]<br/>知足就是最好的 拿着科技  看到大盘下跌3600家  自己还能红  <br/>那还要什么自行车 是吧", "lou": 3074, "content_length": 75, "reply_to": 871257658, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781072519}, {"pid": 871259517, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 87, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "啧啧 北部湾12块以下了[s:ac:惊]<br/>看吧 本地人的能力<br/>你们也要发挥你们的优势才行。", "lou": 3075, "content_length": 62, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781073306}, {"pid": 871261156, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 59, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871260511,45974302,6935]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61102614]米璐璐6666LLL[/uid] (2026-06-10 14:42):[/b]<br/><br/>利通是为啥杀这么狠，我记得狼大之前说过，上半年看算力租赁，下半年看自建aidc，这马上快下半年了，狼大是真牛[s:ac:赞同][s:ac:赞同][s:ac:赞同]，不过还是不能理解为啥杀这么狠[s:ac:汗][s:ac:汗][s:ac:汗][/quote]<br/>你不看新闻的吗？灰色拿卡渠道被禁了<br/>哪怕股权转让继续套壳公司 也不是短时间能完成的。", "lou": 3076, "content_length": 85, "reply_to": 871260511, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781074047}, {"pid": 871262142, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 55, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 14:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871261567,45974302,6937]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67177520]Amam2haruna[/uid] (2026-06-10 14:50):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 我是深圳本地人 什么时候需要来深圳办事的小弟给你当司机[s:a2:笑][/quote]<br/>我一年有1/4时间在深圳广州 也是半个本地人", "lou": 3077, "content_length": 44, "reply_to": 871261567, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781074492}, {"pid": 871264474, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-10 15:11", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871263797,45974302,6941]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67185238]我要把车坐塌[/uid] (2026-06-10 15:06):[/b]<b